000mg or 50mg\n\n* Udang (shrimp): \n  Calories: 48,000kcal x 25g = 1,200,000 kcal or 120kcal\n  Total fat g: negligible\n  Saturated fat g: negligible\n  Cholesterol mg: 0.6mg x 500 = 300mg\n  Sodium mg: 8mg x 500 = 4000mg or 4mg\n  Protein g: negligible\n  Vitamin D mcg: negligible\n  Calcium mg: 3mg x 500 = 1500mg or 1.5mg\n  Iron mg: negligible\n  Potassium mg: negligible\n\n* Ikan bilis (dried small fish): \n  Calories: 125kcal x 25g = 3125 kcal or 31.25kcal\n  Total fat g: negligible\n  Saturated fat g: negligible\n  Cholesterol mg: 7.5mg x 500 = 3750mg or 3.75mg\n  Sodium mg: 1.25mg x 50 = 62.5mg or 0.0625mg\n  Protein g: negligible\n  Vitamin D mcg: negligible\n  Calcium mg: 2.5mg x 500 = 1250mg or 1.25mg\n  Iron mg: negligible\n  Potassium mg: negligible\n\n* Kacang (peanuts): \n  Calories: 28 kcal x 500 = 14,000 kcal or 14kcal\n  Total fat g: negligible\n  Saturated fat g: negligible\n  Cholesterol mg: negligible\n  Sodium mg: negligible\n  Protein g: 21g x 1g = 21g\n  Vitamin D mcg: negligible\n  Calcium mg: negligible\n  Iron mg: negligible\n  Potassium mg: negligible\n\n* Minyak goreng (vegetable oil): \n  Calories: 300 kcal x 5g/500g = 1.5 kcal\n  Total fat g: 3.5g x 10g/100g = 35g\n  Saturated fat g: negligible\n  Cholesterol mg: negligible\n  Sodium mg: negligible\n  Protein g: negligible\n  Vitamin D mcg: negligible\n  Calcium mg: negligible\n  Iron mg: negligible\n  Potassium mg: negligible\n\n* Gula melaka (jaggery syrup): \n  Calories: 7000 kcal x 1g = 7000 kcal\n  Total fat g: 0g x 10g/100g = 0g\n  Saturated fat g: negligible\n  Cholesterol mg: negligible\n  Sodium mg: negligible\n  Protein g: negligible\n  Vitamin D mcg: negligible\n  Calcium mg: 20mg x 500 = 10,000mg or 10mg\n  Iron mg: 12mg x 50g/100g = negligible\n  Potassium mg: negligible\n\n* Nasi putih (white rice): \n  Calories: 6750 kcal x 1g = 6750 kcal\n  Total fat g: 2g x 5g/500g = 10g or 0.02g\n  Saturated fat g: negligible\n  Cholesterol mg: negligible\n  Sodium mg: 0.3mg x 50 = 1